{"tid":854263,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【C朗涉姦】隨時引渡　律師建議C朗着草？","createTime":"2018-10-09T08:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T23:48:06.000Z","uid":54373,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"636105ea8016b3f4be4eb41fef983df785a9d738","tid":854263,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:52:21.000Z","msg":"C朗拿度涉嫌強姦案備受關注，英國《每日鏡報》引述法律專家分析，美國法院隨時會發出引渡令，將身處歐洲嘅C朗拿度拘捕去美國受審，C朗如果唔想有呢個結果，唯一方法就係返去葡萄牙。西班牙著名律師哥迪斯表示：「美國同歐洲嘅法律唔同，只要C朗拿度唔喺只己嘅國家(葡萄牙)，美國法院就有權向佢引渡番去受審。」C朗拿度喺葡萄牙勁旅士砵亭出道，雖然佢曾經透露過願意返去母會掛靴，不過佢今夏先至同祖雲達斯簽約4年，相信仍會喺意大利留一段日子。"},{"pid":"338848a578b0a48b32b8fbf31804080baf5aaa33","tid":854263,"uid":5649,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:38:11.000Z","msg":"去土耳其安塔利亞同羅賓奴組成最強皇馬強姦鋒線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4abda7903691726666ceae8a1662a4d68c292e","tid":854263,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"338848a578b0a48b32b8fbf31804080baf5aaa33","tid":854263,"uid":5649,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:38:11.000Z","msg":"去土耳其安塔利亞同羅賓奴組成最強皇馬強姦鋒線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:40:23.000Z","msg":"左強姦，又雞姦？"},{"pid":"5ba95a5ecf38fc81996c70e75cc5fb40a1ab0710","tid":854263,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6a4abda7903691726666ceae8a1662a4d68c292e","tid":854263,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"338848a578b0a48b32b8fbf31804080baf5aaa33","tid":854263,"uid":5649,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:38:11.000Z","msg":"去土耳其安塔利亞同羅賓奴組成最強皇馬強姦鋒線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:40:23.000Z","msg":"左強姦，又雞姦？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:41:12.000Z","msg":"羅賓奴好似係輪姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a4def04d48ac88989376452853e30fd64cbe17"